sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Producer as Inbox dispatch
    participant Channel as IInboxHandlerCommitChannel
    participant Worker as InboxHandlerWorker
    participant Coord as IWorkCoordinator
    participant DB as Postgres

    Note over Producer,Channel: 5 handlers complete in close succession
    Producer->>Channel: EnqueueAsync(handler1 result)
    Producer->>Channel: EnqueueAsync(handler2 result)
    Producer->>Channel: EnqueueAsync(handler3 result)
    Producer->>Channel: EnqueueAsync(handler4 result)
    Producer->>Channel: EnqueueAsync(handler5 result)

    Note over Worker: BatchFlusher coalesces (25ms window OR 100 max OR 50 immediate threshold)
    Worker->>Worker: Drain channel into batch
    Worker->>Coord: CommitHandlerBatchAsync([5 results])
    Coord->>DB: SELECT * FROM commit_handler_batch($jsonb)

    Note over DB: Single outer transaction
    loop For each handler in array
        DB->>DB: BEGIN (implicit savepoint)
        alt Handler succeeds
            DB->>DB: process_inbox_completions + store_outbox + event_store + perspective_event auto-create
            DB->>DB: RELEASE SAVEPOINT
            DB->>DB: RETURN ROW(handler_id, true, NULL)
        else Handler throws
            DB->>DB: ROLLBACK TO SAVEPOINT (siblings unaffected)
            DB->>DB: RETURN ROW(handler_id, false, SQLERRM)
        end
    end

    DB->>DB: COMMIT (single fsync covers all successes)
    opt Any inserts emitted
        DB->>DB: pg_notify('wh_work', '<category>') fires post-COMMIT (deduped)
    end
    DB-->>Coord: 5 result rows

    Coord-->>Worker: IReadOnlyList<HandlerBatchResult>
    Note over Worker: Per-result fan-out
    loop For each failed result
        Worker->>Worker: Route to IFailureChannel for retry
    end
